 Daniel Coming Back

Okay, i've been reading other forums about Daniel's return and it seems like lots of fans DON'T LIKE THE IDEA. I guess some of us think it's NOT A GOOD MOVE FOR THE SHOW.

What do we think??

Personally, I GLAD Daniel's coming back and I think it's the best move for the show. Daniel's departure for me made me not like the show as much, even Jonas couldn't fit the shoes, but now that I know he's coming back I can be happy.

Michael Shanks is a great actor too! Probably the best. He decision to come back is a good one and I hope the fans don't go crazy and say he SHOULDN'T have.


What do you guys think???
